What benefits OpenSea gives to me?

Instantly find matching positions

As soon as you've placed a position, the web-application shows you suitable ones. Easily choose the best & send offer. You will also get an email notification once somebody opens new one suitable for you.

Choose best freight rates

From now charterers and brokers can place cargoes with freight idea.
Shipowners are able to add named tonnage without risk of its disclosure. All ships and cargoes are depersonalized until you'll start firm negotiations.

Fix online & on the go

Get offers, discuss terms & fix charter party online. Start your firm negotiations and send a final recap or ship’s docs or whatever you need in a single chat. All information available from anywhere & any device.

Realtime worldwide map

Watch actual state of the world freight market.
Real positions in any port of the world.
Every inquiry is from your colleague or potential new client.
